## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
make install

# Seed sample data
make seed

# Start the application
make start
```

- **Backend:** http://localhost:8000
- **Frontend:** http://localhost:3000

## Architecture

```
{{ project_slug }}/
├── backend/          FastAPI + {{ framework_display_name }}
├── frontend/         Next.js + Chakra UI v3
├── cypher/           LadybugDB schema DDL
├── data/             Domain ontology, generated documents & LadybugDB data
├── .env              Configuration (not tracked in git)
├── .env.example      Configuration template
└── Makefile          Development commands
```

